⚙️ Setup Instructions
Ensure you have a Google Cloud Project set up before proceeding.

1. Prerequisites
Flutter SDK (Latest version)
Google Cloud CLI
Gemini API Key (via Google AI Studio)
2. Installation
Clone the Repo:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/antigravity.git
cd antigravity
Configure Environment Variables:
Create a .env file in the root directory. Do not hardcode keys.
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_id
Run the App:
flutter pub get
flutter run
